description: The mini Display Port to HDMI Adapter lets you connect a high definition monitor, projector, or LCD that uses a HDMI connector or cable to a MacBook, MacBook Pro, or MacBook Air with a mini Display Port. Compatible With Apple: iMac / Mac Mini / Mac Pro / MacBook Air / MacBook Pro 13 inch / MacBook Pro 15 inch / MacBook Pro 17 inche.NOTE: Adapter only works with laptops with Mini Display port, please check with your devices output specification before placing order. NOTE: Audio function is NOT supported on all models released before April 2010.
title: eForCity TOTHMDPHDMMF Mini Display Port Thunderbolt Port to HDMI HD TV Cable Lead Adapter for Apple
